00:21:17,900 --> 00:21:22,460
So, what are the advantages of this on-policy evaluation?

426
00:21:24,080 --> 00:21:29,680
Well, the most fundamental difference here is that...

427
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:32,580
The evaluation mode, uh, is basically the mode of evaluation.

