00:21:52,860 --> 00:21:54,920
In fact, it influences the direction of the conversation.

437
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:58,660
And this, in turn, will affect the content of its subsequent memory.

438
00:21:58,660 --> 00:22:00,440
So, our on-policy...

