00:22:13,790 --> 00:22:17,960
can provide some additional, uh, diagnostic feedback,

445
00:22:17,960 --> 00:22:19,140
or optimization signals,

446
00:22:19,140 --> 00:22:22,800
This could also potentially guide the improvement of the agent's own memory strategy.

447
00:22:22,800 --> 00:22:23,850
optimization.

